snippet: Donald Brown ran for two touchdowns, Andrew Luck added another and the visiting Indianapolis Colts rallied yet again, this time beating the Tennessee Titans, 30-27, on Thursday.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Indianapolis Colts beat Tennessee Titans, 30-27; other football news noted.
